    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      OASIS Wound Matrix (Oasis) will be applied to wounds, with sequential biopsy of healing
      wounds to explore the mechanism of action.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Wound types will be Diabetic Foot Ulcers (DFU) and Venous Stasis Ulcers (VSU).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
